Views: This report only has a grid view. Query: This report data is built from a Database Query. Use this report to evaluate Precision Queue performance and staffing. Precision Queue Interval provides key statistics per Precision Queue such as average speed of answer and contacts handled, as well as agent state times. The Precision Queue interval report is comparable to Peripheral Skill Group Historical. Precision Queue Interval All Fields
